          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18989854-krystal?shelf=horror">horror</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18989854-krystal?shelf=freebies-and-gifts">freebies-and-gifts</a>, 
