<div id="review_1002719819" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1002719819" />
    <a title="Melissa ♥ Dog/Wolf Lover ♥ Martin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17438949-melissa-dog-wolf-lover-martin"><img alt="Melissa ♥ Dog/Wolf Lover ♥ Martin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1607553912p2/17438949.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1002719819?book_show_action=true">Jul 21, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Melissa ♥ Dog/Wolf Lover ♥ Martin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Melissa ♥ Dog/Wolf Lover ♥ Martin" href="/user/show/17438949-melissa-dog-wolf-lover-martin">Melissa ♥ Dog/Wolf Lover ♥ Martin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780615610054" href="/book/show/13569434-carmilla">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/17438949-melissa-dog-wolf-lover-martin?shelf=own">own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1002719819" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9257542700310590355">I got this book upon watching a movie on Netflix called, &quot;The Moth Diaries&quot;. One of the classes the girls were in, the teacher passed this book out for them to read and review. And of course, I had to order a copy. <br/><br/>I thought it was pretty good for a short novella on vampires. It was a very different take and I did enjoy it. </span>
  <span id="freeText9257542700310590355" style="display:none">I got this book upon watching a movie on Netflix called, "The Moth Diaries". One of the classes the girls were in, the teacher passed this book out for them to read and review. And of course, I had to order a copy. <br /><br />I thought it was pretty good for a short novella on vampires. It was a very different take and I did enjoy it. </span>
  <a data-text-id="9257542700310590355" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


